data.description: Rare find! Row-end townhome in Daybreak just 2 blocks from the lake where you can paddleboard, kayak, and canoe!!! Highly desirable 2-car garage, beautiful designer finishes throughout, LARGE open main level floor plan with soaring floor to ceiling windows drawing in all the natural light. Hardwood flooring throughout the main level. All newer stainless appliances, granite countertops, large island, breakfast nook, and vaulted ceilings. Enjoy your own private and peaceful fenced patio/courtyard, perfect for entertaining or pets. Upstairs includes all three bedrooms, two full baths as well as the laundry. The primary suite has AMAZING views of the mountains, with walk-in closet, dual shower heads, and European glass shower doors. Downstairs has a family room large enough for multi- purpose (home gym, Office, 4th bedroom). This space also has an unfinished closed off area that has been plumbed for a 4th bathroom and is large enough for a 4th bedroom. Miles of biking and walking trails, dog parks, playgrounds, tennis and pickleball courts, pools, and splash pads. Located close to the new neighborhood Harmons grocery store, Soda Row, restaurants, and shops. The amenities that Daybreak has to offer are endless. Schedule your private showing today!
